ABOUT US

Balkonnect Festival

The Balkonnect Festival 2025 is the premier event bridging the Western Balkans’ leading industries with global innovation, networking, matchmaking, and investment opportunities. Held annually, this year’s festival will focus on innovation, transformation, e-solutions and investment, including sectorial experiences, AI, big data, and green economies. It is expected to attract key stakeholders from sectors including wood-metal/construction, tourism-agri-food-processing, outsourcing, ICT & Digital, renewable and green, banking and finance etc.
